Files:

create.py [N]   - creates LXC configurations for N nodes
generate.py [N] - generates configurations for N node
run.py -c [N]   - runs N nodes on N containers
destroy_all.sh  - destroys all LXC containers

To use LXC containers put this in your networking interfaces:

auto eth0
iface eth0 inet static
    address 0.0.0.0

auto br0
iface br0 inet dhcp
	bridge_ports eth0
